org.rpgleparser.api.LFLD

Class FLDL0100

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rpgleparser.api.LFLD.FLDL0100
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, FLDLoutputFormat, IFLDL0100
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FLDL0200

    public class FLDL0100
extends java.lang.Object
implements IFLDL0100, FLDLoutputFormat, java.io.Serializable
    A data transfer object with conversion capabilities from AS400 Byte[]. This one implements the data format described in the QUSLFLD FLDL0100 format.
    Author:
    Eric N. Wilson
